--- Menasor / Dead-End / Drag Strip / Astroblast ---

Incarcinator's charges crash into Menasor's head. The Stunticons 
come to a general agreement, time to disband. 

Dead-End and Drag Strip hit the ground running, "Lets get out of 
here!" Yells Dead-End. He and Drag Strip transform into car mode, 
and rip over the hill they came form, heading towards the 
Decepticon base, the Dark Avian.

---------------------------------------

Astroblast crosses the Atlantic, and continues on to Hudson's 
Bay. He, Megatron, Switchblade, and Fireblade's remains arrive at 
the Dark Avian. Astroblast's hatch opens up. Switchblade hops 
out, and enters the Dark Avian.
